 be accompanied by a point, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When present, this property takes precedence over ","type":"text"},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textVariableAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"code":"textRadialOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"syntax":"json","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"code":"[0, 4]","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[3, 0]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is only applied to the style if "},{"type":"codeVo